{"tid":754612,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古代嘅女人會唔會脫毛？","createTime":"2018-07-24T14:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T07:18:07.000Z","uid":60727,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"640ce700647b5ae01af08312dac998ea475c49fa","tid":754612,"uid":60727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"會嘅又會用咩脫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e32de9cb9cd73c09d361ec76c615a94262cbe25","tid":754612,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"徒手抆"},{"pid":"b1902a04ee70b43600e24d5bd71792686cf53de0","tid":754612,"uid":147789,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"攞青龍偃月刀斬"},{"pid":"d59ecbfd66e9ab2f4d646aabf1dec66c0d21ecbe","tid":754612,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"叫奴隸幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申做過"},{"pid":"57691566d46bdf1ab3f83ddaab9161f85272ada2","tid":754612,"uid":60727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9722662abf7500dd7b37fa3b93e78d30b7292a4a","tid":754612,"uid":64578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"而家啲大陸女人都係唔剃毛，你估下古代果啲脫唔脫？"},{"pid":"07a6b05413c0c619f56c41b7074e0168f51dd3c0","tid":754612,"uid":138696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"同「挽面」一樣掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b407cf6f4acc28b6801aed50765cf7181123ab82","tid":754612,"uid":191073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"燒"},{"pid":"613b20b5b12caffd14d3bd09d257107a8c2783c8","tid":754612,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n女人脫毛係大概100年前先開始有嘅事"},{"pid":"717c125ad09f53c13138ccc172fc4e1f82343964","tid":754612,"uid":60727,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"係知乎揾到，勿屌簡體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n古代哲学观念里有一个很重要的思想，就是&ldquo;平衡&rdquo;。在体毛上来说，除了挽面，古代妇女是不剃体毛的，既不多也不少的体毛才是女性（尤其是大家闺秀）身体健康的表现。典型例子现在被现代医学称为&ldquo;多囊卵巢综合症&rdquo;，被香港龙虎豹杂志叫做&ldquo;白虎&rdquo;（人为剃掉）的现象，在唐代以后的相书里就是被视为不详的女性。多毛症女性虽然没有特别被相书提及，但相书里还是有些语句说到某部位多毛不好，克夫怎么的，而且医书里还有一些方剂是为了祛除某部位毛发的，这就涉及到病症，不在讨论范围里了。"},{"pid":"35ea258332deb2fd160e29441d06cf0b0a467a58","tid":754612,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"面毛一定會 其他位就睇人"},{"pid":"61a38ff3e8d837f301a73b2e4feb7b6760d1cd39","tid":754612,"uid":60727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ea258332deb2fd160e29441d06cf0b0a467a58","tid":754612,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"面毛一定會 其他位就睇人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"但又話身體髮膚受之父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b30c7be3cdbbff5f6f4a6074432d36d9b3dd956","tid":754612,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn-wpmsa.defymedia.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2012/10/Shes-holding-a-lamp-and-making-a-brave-face.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-wpmsa.defymedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2012%2F10%2FShes-holding-a-lamp-and-making-a-brave-face.jpg&h=34ba56e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古希臘掹緊毛既女人<br />\n用既係呢樣嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-us-east-2.amazonaws.com/orbitz-media/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/16131633/orbitz_national-seashell-day-colors.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-east-2.amazonaws.com%2Forbitz-media%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%